Join the #PotateYourPet contest for a chance to win a memelist from @memeland!
-
How to join:
1. Follow our pages @barked @meowed, like this post and become a member in the MEMELAND discord server (link in bio)
2. Remix this Reel surrounding your pet with ‘potatoes’
3. Remember to post it on Instagram with #PotateYourPet
4. Creativity is a bonus 
5. Only one submission per account allowed. We will not consider entries by account with more than 1 submission.
6. If you don’t follow the instructions you will be disqualified.
